Content-Type: text/plain; charset=utf-8

Team,

After reviewing the projections and the customer interviews from last week, I'm going to recommend we ship the new pricing in Q3 with a single Pro tier at $19/month. We'll keep Free as-is and drop the old Team tier since less than 4% of accounts are on it.

The reasoning:
- Pro at $19 captures the heavy-individual-user we kept losing to Superhuman.
- Single-tier is simpler to communicate and collapses our paywall logic.
- We'll grandfather existing Team subs through end of year.

I'd like to lock this on Friday so marketing has time to prep the launch site. Please push back today if you disagree.

Ana

